The paper proposes a deep learning-based method for rain removal from images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also introduces a novel network architecture and adversarial training, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of gradient information, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
